snippet.title: MISS PAP X AMBER ROSS GILL HAUL | BRUTALLY HONEST!!
snippet.description:
Hi guys I'm back with another video and this time I'm trying out Amber from Love Island 2019 collection with Miss Pap. I picked a large range of items from trousers to dresses to shorts, to find out how good this collection was. As per usual everything is linked below, hope you enjoy!

J x
